  [Text] Panama City, 19 May (AFP) -- Foreign Minister Jose 
Raul Mulino today reported that the Panamanian Government has 
approved the appointment of Robert Pastor, whom U.S. President 
Bill Clinton will name to replace Deane Hinton at the U.S. 
Embassy in Panama City. 
