<H3> <TI>   Castro Holds News Conference at Tourism Convention </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Castro Holds News Conference at Tourism Convention </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL2105014894 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in 
