<H3> <TI>   PRC Ambasador Visits Genetic Engineering Center </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PRC Ambasador Visits Genetic Engineering Center </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL2005175994 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1406 GMT 
20 May 94 </F>

