<H3> <TI>   Colombian Ambassador Notes Development of Ties </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Colombian Ambassador Notes Development of Ties </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL2105182394 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1700 
GMT 21 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2105182394 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Colombian Ambassador to Cuba Ricardo Santamaria has 
said that, over the past few hours, important events have taken 
place in the development of efforts by Colombia and Cuba to 
expand their economic and friendly ties. Among these, he 
included the visit of the Colombian vice minister for economic 
development with a delegation of businessmen, and the signing of 
a document by the civil aviation boards of the two countries 
agreeing to the prompt reestablishment of regular flights 
between Colombia and Cuba. 

</TEXT>

