  [Text] Sao Paulo, 20 May (AE) -- Former Sao Paulo Governor 
Orestes Quercia, presidential candidate of the Brazilian 
Democratic Movement Party [PMDB], today met in his campaign 
headquarters with two incumbent governors and five former 
governors of his party to officially announce that Iris Rezende 
